{
  "stem": "18960.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Scaffold-- I saw they had vessels full of ground raw meat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They have-- they have it ground with onions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the SS love-- liked very much raw meat ground to eat, just like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I noticed that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to go off to get water for our-- for our-- for-- for the work, for the mortar, for-- to mix the mortar with, get water from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, the SS was watching-- are we going, are we coming, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I noticed a Polish woman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- I started, like, from a distance, flirting with her, and she flirted with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as I was going to, with a pail, with two pails, to pick up water, and I saw a pail of meat standing there, I exchanged one pail-- two full of water, one pail of meat.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they didn't notice it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I continued that practice for a while-- one pail of meat, one pail of water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I started not only eating myself, but feeding my whole group.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But after about two or three weeks, the SS noticed that we gained weight sort of.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They knew that something fishy was going on there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they took it out from there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But in the meantime, I made contact with that Polish woman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She knew my name already, my number, the block where-- the barrack where I lived, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she-- as it turned out, she wrote to her parents in Poland, that she would forego her packages if they'll send me the packages there, because she has enough food.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She works in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
